data.description: Beautiful home for sale in the Olde Oaks Golf Club Community! This home features a fantastic living area, stainless steel kitchen appliances, granite counter tops, side entry garage, and a covered back porch with an outstanding view of the golf course. Large master bedroom and fantastic master bath with huge walk in closet, his and hers sinks, whirlpool tub and walk in shower. Brand new roof as of 6/1/18 and the entire home is in pristine condition. This home is a must see! All furniture and appliances are included if requested by buyer. Sales price is open for negotiation.
